 Ticketmaster 承认黑客窃取 5.6 亿客户数据以勒索赎金https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticketmaster-acknowledge-hackers-stealing-560million-customers-data-for-ransom-3762096?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ticketmaster-acknowledge-hackers-stealing-560million-客户数据勒索Anagricel DuranMon, 03 Jun 2024 19:35:14 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3762096 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Ticketmaster 徽标显示在智能手机上，背景中可以看到 Ticketmaster 网页主页。 （乔纳森·拉阿/NurPhoto 来自 Getty Images 拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>根据 SEC 文件，该公司于 5 月 20 日发现数据库存在未经授权的活动</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticketmaster-acknowledge-hackers-stealing-560million-customers-data-for-ransom-3762096">Ticketmaster 承认黑客窃取 5.6 亿客户数据以勒索赎金的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Ticketmaster 徽标显示在智能手机上，背景中可以看到 Ticketmaster 网页主页。 （乔纳森·拉阿/NurPhoto 拍摄，盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ticketmaster-stock-image-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Ticketmaster 的母公司 Live Nation 承认其用户数据遭受了数据泄露。</p><p>根据<em><a href="https://hackread.com/hackers-ticketmaster-data-breach-560m-users-sale/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hackread</a></em> （来自<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/ticketmaster-hack-group-stole-data-560m-customers/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Billboard</a></em> ）的一份报告，数据泄露是由一个名为 ShinyHunters 的知名黑客组织实施的，他们声称从 Ticketmaster 窃取了 1.3 TB 的数据。</p><p>从 5.6 亿客户获得的详细信息包括全名、地址、电子邮件地址、电话号码、门票销售和活动详细信息、订单信息和部分支付卡数据。他们威胁要以 500,000 美元（393,800 英镑）的价格出售这些数据。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticketmaster-urges-users-to-carry-out-checks-as-560million-customers-data-stolen-and-held-ransom-by-hackers-3760885">由于数据泄露，票务公司此前敦促用户进行检查。</a> </p><figure id="attachment_3760889" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3760889" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3760889" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ticketmaster@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2022 年 11 月 18 日，电脑屏幕上显示 Ticketmaster 网站" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ticketmaster@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ticketmaster@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ticketmaster@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ticketmaster@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ticketmaster@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ticketmaster@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3760889" class="wp-caption-text"> 2022 年 11 月 18 日，电脑屏幕上显示售票员网站。图片来源：Joe Raedle/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Live Nation 现已在周五（5 月 31 日） <a href="https://www.sec.gov/ix?doc=/Archives/edgar/data/0001335258/000133525824000081/lyv-20240520.htm" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" data-type="link" data-id="https://www.sec.gov/ix?doc=/Archives/edgar/data/0001335258/000133525824000081/lyv-20240520.htm">向 SEC 提交的</a>文件中证实了此事。根据文件，该公司于 5 月 20 日发现数据库存在未经授权的活动，并开始展开调查。他们表示已通知并正在配合执法部门。</p><p> Ticketmaster 在文件中表示，此次违规行为“尚未，而且我们认为不太可能对我们的整体业务运营、财务状况或运营业绩产生重大影响。”</p><p>据<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/ticketmaster-data-breach-sec-filing-1235030951/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》</em></a>报道，一位知情人士透露，目前没有证据表明帐户凭据被泄露。</p><p>该文件还表示，此次泄露发生在“包含公司数据的第三方云数据库环境”，而不是 Ticketmaster 的服务器上。</p><p> Ticketmaster 向<em>滚石杂志</em>证实，<em> </em>这是该公司通过云数据公司 Snowflake 托管的数据库。该文件没有提供任何可能导致数据泄露的细节。</p><p>就在有关数据泄露的报道发布几天前，联合司法部对 Live Nation 提起了大规模的反垄断诉讼，并声称这家票务巨头采取了滥用措施来消除美国的竞争。 </p><figure id="attachment_3457270" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3457270" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3457270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo.jpg" alt="在这张照片插图中，智能手机上显示了 Ticketmaster 徽标。图片来源：Mateusz Slodkowski/GETTY" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3457270" class="wp-caption-text">在这张照片插图中，智能手机上显示了 Ticketmaster 徽标。图片来源：Mateusz Slodkowski/GETTY</figcaption></figure><p>网络安全公司 ESET 的全球网络安全顾问 Jake Moore 告诉<em>《太阳报》</em> ，他建议 Ticketmaster 客户尽快更改网站密码。他还敦促用户留意该公司询问信息的后续电子邮件。</p><p> “这次极其严重的泄露事件中涉及大量高度个人数据，这让所有相关人员更加担忧。 Ticketmaster 选择不支付赎金，随着善后清理工作的改善，这种情况逐渐变得越来越普遍。”他说。</p><p> “由于敏感信息现在正在出售，受影响的人必须格外小心，更改密码并避开声称来自公司并索要信息的后续电子邮件、短信和电话。引人注目的数据泄露可能会对客户产生长期影响，包括身份盗窃和财务欺诈。”</p><p> Ticketmaster 的其他消息是，去年 10 月，该<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticketmaster-announce-plan-to-allow-fans-to-contribute-directly-to-music-venue-trust-3512583">公司宣布了一项新计划，允许粉丝直接向音乐场馆信托基金 (MVT) 捐款，</a>以帮助支持英国草根场馆。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticketmaster-acknowledge-hackers-stealing-560million-customers-data-for-ransom-3762096">Ticketmaster 承认黑客窃取 5.6 亿客户数据以勒索赎金的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
